Package eu.wauz.wauzcore.system.util

This package contains general util classes, which are used everywhere in the engine.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Chance
    An util class for getting values for rng stuff.
    ChunkKeyMap<T>
    A tool to map chunks to objects.
    Components
    Util class for interacting with adventure components.
    Cooldown
    An util class for getting and setting cooldowns.
    DeprecatedUtils
    An util class for usage of unsave or deprecated methods.
    Formatters
    A collection of different decimal formatters.
    UnicodeUtils
    An util class for stuff like unicode icons.
    WauzDateUtils
    An util class for calculating dates.
    WauzFileUtils
    An util class to read or modify files.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    WauzMode
    An util class to determine the mode of entities or worlds.
